[[File:Infantryman_in_1942_with_M1_Garand,_Fort_Knox,_KY.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:Ethiopian_Soldiers_Korean_War.jpg|thumb]]（左）與M1加蘭德步槍（右）參與[[韓戰|韓戰]]的埃塞俄比亞士兵，攝於1953年]]
[[File:Honor_Guard_of_ROCAF_standing_at_National_Revolutionary_Martyr's_Shrine_20081221.jpg|thumb]]禮兵]]
